{"tid":627611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩警掃黃期間 涉順手牽羊偷妓女$3000被捕","createTime":"2018-04-13T06:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T22:55:54.000Z","uid":5195,"like":849,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"788f3d0bb431e30830709c60664a204664192b37","tid":627611,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"警隊懷疑有人監守自盜，兩名警員涉嫌在掃黃行動中偷妓女錢被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，警方東區特別職務隊人員，本周初進行一項掃黃行動，拘捕多名涉嫌賣淫女子。警員將被捕女子帶返警署調查期間，懷疑有人順手牽羊，偷去妓女銀包內3000元，稍後警員替她們進行俗稱「打包頭」的程序，即將她們身上的物件放入袋內收起，有妓女發現銀包內的3000元不翼而飛，即時向警員舉報。<br />\n<br />\n警方翻看cctv，拍下有人偷竊，事後拘捕涉案兩名特別職務隊警員，案件已港島總區重案組跟進調查。"},{"pid":"66af522be0ced2445a7c306e09c1fe5a957f32c7","tid":627611,"uid":118125,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"加兩分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1949422f2d13272c57abf4ac320616cea2be57b2","tid":627611,"uid":74272,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"今次唔係休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e27385d497f6f332483ff8fcb643411c6cd593","tid":627611,"uid":31389,"like":432,"dislike":1,"score":431,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"血汗錢都偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1691969e12623f3dac9a906604405f979a152d9","tid":627611,"uid":59283,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"警方強調呢"},{"pid":"c38f0731b65a1cfeb3713d9a319dc0497a2e7c9d","tid":627611,"uid":21222,"like":243,"dislike":3,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"肉錢都偷，無道德"},{"pid":"52bb403be3850354c5d1ff1967150d76f8d1a0c7","tid":627611,"uid":81756,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":13